DataElement.preferredName: Registration Service Research Resource Telecommunication Address ISO21090.TEL.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A sequence of digits or characters used to identify a particular telephone, fax, or email of a registration center. EXAMPLE(S): The phone number to call to request that a subject be registered and randomized on a study.
